I"Ï—<img src="/assets/BlueCat/Axiom/Axiom.png" alt="Axiom">
<div class="image-caption">Axiom</div>

<p>Blue Cat is delivering their new product ‚ÄòAxiom‚Äô soon and I‚Äôm here having a blast with it. This will be the first solo plugin review I‚Äôm doing, despite having reviewed 100s of plugins already (in DAW reviews).</p>

<p>Axiom is mainly targeted as a guitar system, however it‚Äôs also an great multi-effects solution for any sort of sound.</p>

<p>I was provided an early NFR (not for resale) review copy.</p>

<p>As of this writing‚Ä¶ this is the first review I know of about Axiom. It‚Äôs currently not released yet (and I do have permission to release this).</p>

<p>Let‚Äôs get on with the review!</p>

<p><strong>UPDATED</strong> Updated for Axiom 1.1.</p>

<!--more-->

<p><strong>If you have any questions or comments, please comment below! I read every comment and respond to most.</strong> No registration is necessary to comment, so don‚Äôt be shy.</p>

