<p>Reverb isn‚Äôt special, but it doesn‚Äôt suck either. I generally expect every reverb to be an awful metallic mess, but it‚Äôs not. I‚Äôd even be tempted to use this alone as a mix reverb if I didn‚Äôt already own far too many reverb plugins.</p>

<p>That‚Äôs it. I‚Äôm just here to say that it isn‚Äôt awful. That‚Äôs a bold statement for an included reverb effect.</p>

