<p>I am a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ibanez_Tube_Screamer">Tube Screamer</a> lover. This is disappointing. It‚Äôs kinda tube screamery, like a modern TS-9 in a way. I can‚Äôt really nail down what it reminds me of‚Ä¶ but it‚Äôs none of my tube screamers.</p>

<p>Luckily you can use VST/VST3/AU plugins and purchase <a href="https://cytomic.com/scream">the best tubescreamer emulation on the market</a>. The Scream is amazing, and you can mod the pedal <em>in realtime</em> across the whole schematic. Currently a new GUI is in the works that is just amazing.</p>

