<p>The <a href="https://www.boss.info/us/products/ds-1/">Boss DS-1</a> is arguably the most iconic pedal of 90s. I have a handful of them, with various mods, and I used them heavily for about a decade and a half.</p>

<p>‚ÄòOrange Dist‚Äô comes surprisingly close to a stock DS-1. The tone control sounds a bit off, but it‚Äôs not a big deal.</p>

<p>Cool.</p>

<h4 id="waveshaper">Waveshaper</h4>

